1. *Čitala* sam knjigu celo popodne. (I was *reading* a book all afternoon.)
2. Ona *čitala* vesti dok je čekala autobus. (She was *reading* the news while waiting for the bus.)
3. Kada sam bila mala, često sam *čitala* bajke. (When I was a child, I used to *read* fairy tales a lot.)
4. *Čitala* bih novine da imam više vremena. (I would *read* newspapers if I had more time.)
5. Ne sviđa mi se kako on *čita* svoju prezentaciju. (I don't like how he *reads* his presentation.)
6. Ona je veoma brzo *čitala* knjigu. (She was *reading* the book very quickly.)
7. *Čitanje* knjiga je moj omiljeni hobi. (Reading books is my favorite hobby.)
8. Molim te, da mi *pročitaš* ovaj pasus naglas. (Please, *read* this paragraph aloud to me.)
9. Nisam *pročitala* ceo roman, ali mi se sviđa do sada. (I haven't *read* the whole novel, but I like it so far.)
10. Treba mi malo vremena da *pročitam* ovu knjigu. (I need some time to *read* this book.)